channel.description: Ok this is a question relating to pictures. For example u know how jagex has pictures of those scrolls like maps when u click em a pic pops up is thier a way for us to do that with scrolls or clues? if so can u plz tell me the link to thread or inform me on how to do it, if not please dont call me a noob -.- i had pepole do that and its just not right i consider that spam. Thank you as always for your time to read this and help or tell me it doesn't exsist yet. i know it works on private clients.
